      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643585/RenderManforHoudini_TeapotKit_small.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433116632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643585/RenderManforHoudini_TeapotKit_small.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433116632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643620\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManforHoudini_TeapotKit_small.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643585\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"b3907b6d-2cf9-499f-854a-777b44bf3901\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/></span></p><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">RenderMan supp</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.0px;\" class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">orts a full range of geometric primitives, including </span> <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661419/Polygons\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661419\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">polygons</a> <span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.0px;\" class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">, </span> <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661437/NURBS\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661437\" data-linked-resource-version=\"10\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">NURBS</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661421/Subdivision+Surfaces\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661421\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">subdivision surfaces</a> <span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.0px;\" class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">, </span> <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661233/Curves\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661233\" data-linked-resource-version=\"10\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">curves</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661423/Volumes\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661423\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">volumes</a> <span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.0px;\" class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">, procedurals (Alembic), and </span> <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661425/Implicit+Surfaces\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661425\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">implicit surfaces</a> <span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.0px;\" class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">. </span>Object <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544644181/Instances\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644181\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">instancing</a> <span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.0px;\" class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">is fully supported as well.</span></p><p>Below, each section discusses their usage inside Houdini.</p><p><ul class=\"childpages-macro conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-macro-id=\"7dacbcfe-a8e9-40e1-9f97-760804b65689\" data-macro-name=\"children\"><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544643637/Geometric+Settings\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643637\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Geometric Settings</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544643849/Curves\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643849\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Curves</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544643998/Volumes\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643998\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Volumes</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544644133/Implicit+Surfaces\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644133\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Implicit Surfaces</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544644151/Particles\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644151\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Particles</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544644181/Instances\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644181\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Instances</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544644237/Subdivision+Surfaces\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644237\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Subdivision Surfaces</a></li></ul></p><p><br/></p>"
